Installation instructions for the project.


1. **Clone the Repository**

    ```sh
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/image-segmentation-cuda.git
    cd image-segmentation-cuda
    ```

2. **Build the Project**

    ```sh
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ..
    make
    ```

    OR
    
    ```
    chmod +x run.sh
    ./run.sh